C A L M I N G  O C E A N 🌊
No matter what is going on in the world the ocean always seem to have the calming effect.
I don’t know if it’s the sound of the waves, the beautiful blue salty water, the sand in your feet, endless horizon, the warmth of the sun, maybe all of that and more.

I just know that I when I’m with the ocean I am at peace. ✌🏻 What about you, do you find peace with the ocean?
